data.description:
Discover the perfect blend of comfort and style in this stunning single-family home located in the highly sought-after THE GARDENS community in Gilbert. Boasting 4 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, this residence offers the ideal backdrop for modern family living. Step inside and be greeted by the beautifully updated open-concept living, dining, and family rooms. Light gray tile plank flooring graces all traffic areas, creating an inviting and contemporary atmosphere. New window coverings and updated electric outlets, along with modern lighting fixtures, add a touch of elegance to every space. Bright open kitchen, featuring pristine white cabinetry, a convenient island, and stainless steel appliances. Primary suite on the second level, complete with a spacious walk-in closet and extended sink bathroom vanity. Newer AC unit and a gas water heater, ensuring your comfort and convenience year-round. Grassy shade covered backyard, It's the perfect space to unwind after a long day.
THE GARDENS community is truly unique, with its tree-lined streets, 11 parks, 3 sparkling pools, sand volleyball courts, basketball courts, and an abundance of scenic walking paths. It's a neighborhood designed for an active and vibrant lifestyle.
Conveniently located near the 202 freeway, top-rated schools, and the popular San Tan Village shopping district, you'll have everything you need just moments away.
Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this beautiful home yours today. Act quickly, as homes in this prime location don't stay on the market for long! Come and see it soon!
